          "Esperanto builds 45 words from a simple",
          "grid: 5 prefixes × 9 endings. Learn the",
          "system and you unlock all 45 at once.",
          "",
          "KI-  = question    TI-  = that/the",
          "I-   = some        ĈI-  = every",
          "NENI-= no/none",
          "",
          "-O thing  -U person   -A kind",
          "-E place  -AM time    -AL reason",
          "-EL how   -ES whose   -OM amount",
          "",
          "kio = what?  tio = that   io = something",
          "kie = where? tie = there  ie = somewhere",
          "kiam = when? ĉiam = always  nenie = nowhere",
          "",
