    "header_color": "green",
    "pages": [
      {
        "page": 1,
        "total_pages": 1,
        "content": [
          "MIS- works exactly like English: wrongly,",
          "incorrectly, or in error.",
          "",
          "kompreni → miskompreni (misunderstand)",
          "uzi      → misuzi      (misuse)",
          "diri     → misdiri     (misspeak)",
          "",
          "It applies to any verb. Just add mis-.",
          "Think of all the English words you know:",
          "",
          "misplace, misjudge, mislead, misread,",
          "miscount, misquote, misfire, mislabel,",
          "misinform, mismanage, mistrust, mishear",
          "",
          "Same prefix, same logic, same instinct.",
          "When you see mis- in Esperanto, you",
          "already know what it means."
        ],
        "pronunciation": "Leciono kvardek ses"
      }
    ]
  }
